ate with the GRG properties, suggesting that the current epoch of radio\njets have minimal influence on the nature of their surrounding galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2020 18:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 Jan 2021 08:56:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
